-&gt;-&gt;-&gt; dragon.dead=true // this tells the quest engine that the dragon is now set~flagged as &quot;dead&quot;, but it is invisible to the game player
-&gt;-&gt; }
-&gt; &lt;/fight&gt;
-&gt; &lt;displayverbs type=&quot;simplestringlist&quot;&gt;Fight&lt;/displayverbs&gt;
&lt;/object&gt;

